## Limitations
This report is limited by the availability of recent data, as some sources may not reflect the most current trends. Additionally, the focus is primarily on the United States and global trends, which may not capture regional variations in religious change. The reliance on secondary sources also means that the findings are dependent on the accuracy and comprehensiveness of the original research.

